messages.content:
Validate and prepare ISF filing package for shipment reference: {{input.shipmentReference}}

Agent Code: {{input.agentCode}}

=== ISF 10+2 DATA (UAE to USA) ===

ELEMENT 1 - SELLER:
  Name: {{input.sellerName}}
  Address: {{input.sellerAddress}}

ELEMENT 2 - BUYER:
  Name: {{input.buyerName}}
  Address: {{input.buyerAddress}}

ELEMENT 3 - IMPORTER OF RECORD NUMBER: {{input.importerOfRecordNumber}}

ELEMENT 4 - CONSIGNEE NUMBER: {{input.consigneeNumber}}

ELEMENT 5 - MANUFACTURER/SUPPLIER:
  Name: {{input.manufacturerName}}
  Address: {{input.manufacturerAddress}}

ELEMENT 6 - SHIP-TO PARTY:
  Name: {{input.shipToPartyName}}
  Address: {{input.shipToPartyAddress}}

ELEMENT 7 - COUNTRY OF ORIGIN: {{input.countryOfOrigin}}

ELEMENT 8 - HTS NUMBER: {{input.htsNumber}}

ELEMENT 9 - CONTAINER STUFFING LOCATION: {{input.containerStuffingLocation}}

ELEMENT 10 - CONSOLIDATOR:
  Name: {{input.consolidatorName}}
  Address: {{input.consolidatorAddress}}

=== SHIPPING DETAILS ===
Master Bill of Lading: {{input.masterBillOfLading}}
House Bill of Lading: {{input.houseBillOfLading}}
Vessel Name: {{input.vesselName}}
Voyage Number: {{input.voyageNumber}}
SCAC Code: {{input.scacCode}}
Port of Loading (UAE): {{input.portOfLoading}}
Port of Discharge (USA): {{input.portOfDischarge}}
Estimated Departure: {{input.estimatedDeparture}}
Estimated Arrival: {{input.estimatedArrival}}
Container Number(s): {{input.containerNumbers}}

=== CARGO DETAILS ===
Commodity Description: {{input.commodityDescription}}
Number of Packages: {{input.numberOfPackages}}
Gross Weight (kg): {{input.grossWeightKg}}
Volume (CBM): {{input.volumeCbm}}

Maestro Case ID: {{input.caseId}}

Please validate all fields against ISF 10+2 requirements, produce the complete checklist, calculate the filing deadline, and prepare the ISF package JSON for ACE portal submission. When calling AceIsfFiling, pass the caseId so the PDF is saved under the correct case folder.
